summary: Came up with this beauty after some good feedback from my first upload. Hope you enjoy!~
descriptionHtml:
EDIT: I have discovered that i was using bodychange at the time of making the preset and for some people it is required for the preset to load correctly

This is another preset I came up with on the spur of the moment after putting up my other preset. Its my second upload, If you wanna check out my other one here's the link:http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/80561/?
If you wanna get some more reference check images

Don't download with NMM. Download manually and put the .jslot in Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
and put the nif and dds in the chargen folder one up

Required mods to look the same as in screenshots:
SG Hair: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5ovhttJqGRWZUZsODlENTk1bGs/edit
True Eyes: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?
Freckle Mania: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?
Sevenbase: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36992/?
The Coenaculi: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35677/?


I will do my best to answer any questions left in the comments 

Thank to the creators of the mods above for making mods that led to me making this beauty
author: Lyrinthia
